  Code TEXT,
  Name TEXT,
  Continent TEXT,
  Region TEXT,
  SurfaceArea NUMBER,
  IndepYear NUMBER,
  Population NUMBER,
  LifeExpectancy NUMBER,
  GNP NUMBER,
  GNPOld NUMBER,
  LocalName TEXT,
  GovernmentForm TEXT,
  HeadOfState TEXT,
  Capital NUMBER,
  Code2 TEXT
);

-- No foreign key relationships

gold_sql: SELECT Name ,  SurfaceArea ,  IndepYear FROM country ORDER BY Population LIMIT 1

This query will run on a database whose schema is represented as:

  Orchestra_ID NUMBER,
  Orchestra TEXT,
  Conductor_ID NUMBER,
  Record_Company TEXT,
  Year_of_Founded NUMBER,
  Major_Record_Format TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE conductor (
  Conductor_ID NUMBER,
  Name TEXT,
  Age NUMBER,
  Nationality TEXT,
  Year_of_Work NUMBER
);

CREATE TABLE performance (
  Performance_ID NUMBER,
  Orchestra_ID NUMBER,
  Type TEXT,
  Date TEXT,
  Official_ratings_(millions) NUMBER,
  Weekly_rank TEXT,
  Share TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE show (
  Show_ID NUMBER,
  Performance_ID NUMBER,
  If_first_show OTHERS,
  Result TEXT,
  Attendance NUMBER
);

-- orchestra.Conductor_ID = conductor.Conductor_ID
-- performance.Orchestra_ID = orchestra.Orchestra_ID
-- show.Performance_ID = performance.Performance_ID
